text:
I was at a local game trade shop the other day and a stranger in the store had the Protoman whistle as his ringtone. And I was wearing my Mega Man t-shirt. An instant bond was formed, and this stranger recommended I play Journey to Silius. I told him I had only heard of it from a VGM playlist I regularly listen to. And he asked me if I meant SurpaDarky's. 
I did.
